f'''CREATE TABLE tcpdumpout
                    ({','.join([x+' TEXT NULL' for x in p.groupindex.keys()])})
                '''

f'''INSERT INTO tcpdumpout VALUES
                        ({','.join(['"'+x+'"' if x else 'NULL' for x in m.groupdict().values()])})
                    '''

f'''SELECT proto, COUNT(proto)
                                  FROM tcpdumpout
                                  WHERE src_ip=="183.172.104.52"
                                  GROUP BY proto
                              '''

f'''SELECT proto, SUM(ip_length)
                              FROM tcpdumpout
                              WHERE src_ip=="183.172.104.52"
                              GROUP BY proto
                           '''

r'''SELECT COUNT(*)
                                FROM tcpdumpout
                                WHERE ip_flags=="MF" AND src_ip=="183.172.104.52"
                            '''

r'''SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT id)
                                  FROM tcpdumpout
                                  WHERE ip_flags=="MF" AND src_ip=="183.172.104.52"
                              '''

r'''SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT id)
                                      FROM tcpdumpout
                                      WHERE ip_flags=="+" AND proto=="TCP" AND src_ip=="183.172.104.52"
                                  '''

r'''SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT id)
                                      FROM tcpdumpout
                                      WHERE ip_flags=="+" AND proto=="UDP" AND src_ip=="183.172.104.52"
                                  '''

r'''SELECT SUM(ip_length) 
                              FROM tcpdumpout
                              WHERE src_ip=="183.172.104.52"
                              GROUP BY id
                              ORDER BY SUM(ip_length)
                          '''

r'''SELECT SUM(ip_length)
                               FROM tcpdumpout
                               WHERE proto=="TCP" AND src_ip=="183.172.104.52"
                               GROUP BY id
                               ORDER BY SUM(ip_length)
                           '''

r'''SELECT SUM(ip_length)
                               FROM tcpdumpout
                               WHERE proto=="UDP" AND src_ip=="183.172.104.52"
                               GROUP BY id
                               ORDER BY SUM(ip_length)
                           '''

r'''SELECT src_port
                                  FROM tcpdumpout
                                  WHERE proto=="TCP" AND src_ip=="183.172.104.52"
                                  '''

r'''SELECT src_port
                                      FROM tcpdumpout
                                      WHERE proto=="UDP" AND src_ip=="183.172.104.52"
                                      '''

r'''SELECT src_port, COUNT(src_port)
                                      FROM tcpdumpout
                                      WHERE proto=="TCP" AND src_ip=="183.172.104.52"
                                      GROUP BY src_port 
                                      ORDER BY COUNT(src_port) DESC
                                          '''

r'''SELECT SUM(ip_length) 
                                       FROM tcpdumpout
                                       WHERE proto=="TCP" AND src_port=='''

r'''SELECT dst_port, COUNT(dst_port)
                                          FROM tcpdumpout
                                          WHERE proto=="TCP" AND src_ip=="183.172.104.52"
                                          GROUP BY dst_port 
                                          ORDER BY COUNT(dst_port) DESC
                                              '''

r'''SELECT SUM(ip_length) 
                                           FROM tcpdumpout
                                           WHERE proto=="TCP" AND dst_port=='''

r'''SELECT src_port, COUNT(src_port)
                                  FROM tcpdumpout
                                  WHERE proto=="UDP"  AND src_ip=="183.172.104.52"
                                  GROUP BY src_port 
                                  ORDER BY COUNT(src_port) DESC
                                      '''

r'''SELECT SUM(ip_length) 
                                               FROM tcpdumpout
                                               WHERE proto=="UDP" AND src_port=='''

r'''SELECT dst_port, COUNT(dst_port)
                                      FROM tcpdumpout
                                      WHERE proto=="UDP"  AND src_ip=="183.172.104.52"
                                      GROUP BY dst_port 
                                      ORDER BY COUNT(dst_port) DESC
                                          '''

r'''SELECT SUM(ip_length) 
                                               FROM tcpdumpout
                                               WHERE proto=="UDP" AND dst_port=='''

r'''SELECT tcp_flags ,COUNT(tcp_flags)
                                  FROM tcpdumpout
                                  WHERE proto=="TCP" AND src_ip=="183.172.104.52"
                                  GROUP BY tcp_flags
                                  '''
